channel.title: Gigascape Devolepment team
channel.description:
Okay I need beta testers for my server: Gigascape (pk) V1.0
I really need a team to test updates I do to make it awsome. I will post a link to the download page so you don't have to wait on connection times. I will post an updated link every so often. Plaese post bugs and things that need to be changed on THIS thread.
(Note: to stop leachers [b]I WILL NOT[/b] include .java files only .class) Im looking for about 10-15 testers that know runescape stuff and need to report any bugs eg: when you use a spell you don't use runes!! Post if you want to help... I will post a list of people (in)
